{"tid":959693,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"失眠嘅入𦲷討論下","createTime":"2018-12-28T20:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T15:30:43.000Z","uid":120797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fce5749f4ab0df275fa3732dd77085b4f513ccdf","tid":959693,"uid":120797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:13:20.000Z","msg":"明明好攰，聽日又要早起，點樣祿𦲷祿去都係瞓唔着，醒唔倒遲到都係好奢侈嘅一件事，因為本身就瞓唔到最多5.6個鐘就會扎醒，又難瞓易醒，明明好眼瞓都係醒咗就瞓唔番着。<br />\n<br />\n聽朝六點半要起身，點半閂晒燈到四點手機都冇掂過重特登開埋冷氣都係瞓唔撚倒。<br />\n<br />\n有時真係諗如果有個制可以較幾時開同閂個人就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n除咗睇醫生食藥之外大家有咩方法解決失眠？"},{"pid":"4864c18e8e15a980827b45507e9b8eb6c41c2c89","tid":959693,"uid":186232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:14:47.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46f92eaf6fa0a48ceb4a279621e7eadd3c87f68","tid":959693,"uid":120797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4864c18e8e15a980827b45507e9b8eb6c41c2c89","tid":959693,"uid":186232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:14:47.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:15:58.000Z","msg":"巴打都失開眠？"},{"pid":"fa87589d41b683cb59e97b599aaabd9213fe3333","tid":959693,"uid":186232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b46f92eaf6fa0a48ceb4a279621e7eadd3c87f68","tid":959693,"uid":120797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4864c18e8e15a980827b45507e9b8eb6c41c2c89","tid":959693,"uid":186232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:14:47.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:15:58.000Z","msg":"巴打都失開眠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:18:28.000Z","msg":"日日到朝早先訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},